    <rigor-reason>Cross-solution refactor (LegalWorkspace + shared lib + SpaarkeAi). Touches Daily Briefing infrastructure (hook + component + registration). FR-25/NFR-10 risk surface — standalone LegalWorkspace must continue to render Daily Briefing identically. Multi-file dependency graph.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
