      - Replace the placeholder `buildFoundationalConfig` (or the local placeholder registry) so the Home tab renders Daily Briefing as the default section
      - Build a layout with one row containing Daily Briefing
      - Wire the SectionFactoryContext appropriately (bffBaseUrl, authenticatedFetch via useAiSession or similar — see how the existing code obtains these)
      - Optionally pass an `onRateLimitError` callback that emits SpaarkeAi-side telemetry (TELEMETRY_DAILY_BRIEFING_429 from errorTelemetry.ts task 013)
